Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.util

Provides general utility classes for the MEKON-OWL plugin packages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    O_IRIExtractor
    Responsible for extracting IRIs from CIdentity objects that were constructed with IRIs as their identifiers.
    O_IRINamespaces
    Provides MEKON-OWL specific IRI namespaces and entity IRIs within those namespaces.
    OActionLogger  
    OAnnotationReader
    Responsible for reading annotation-property values from OWL entities.
    ODynamicInstanceIRIs
    Manages the assignment of unique IRIs to a set of OWL-based representaions of dynamic MEKON frames-model instantiations.
    OExactNumberRenderer
    Responsible for rendering concrete MEKON INumber objects representing exact numeric values into OWL OWLLiteral objects.
    OFrameConcepts
    Responsible for finding IRIs of OWL concepts that correspond to particular concept-level frames, or their ancestors.
    OFramesEntities
    Responsible for finding IRIs of OWL entities that correspond to particular concept-level Frames Model (FM) entities of specific types.
    OIdentified
    Represents an entity derived from an object derived from an OWL construct of some type that will be used to generate a Frames Model (FM) entity.
    OIdentity
    Represents the identity for a frames-based object derived from an OWL construct of some type.
    OLabelRenderer
    Renderer for OWL entities that uses the standard OWL-API short-form renderer with the standard RDFS label attribute.
    ONumberRangeRenderer
    Responsible for rendering MEKON CNumber objects representing numeric ranges into OWL OWLDataRange objects.
    OSlotProperties
    Responsible for finding IRIs of OWL properties that correspond to Frames Model (FM) slots.
    OStoredInstanceIRIs
    Manages the assignment of unique IRIs to a set of OWL-based representaions of stored MEKON frames-model instantiations.
    OWLAPIVersion
